source: TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_SEQ_00<tab>Jajakuta the merchant is visibly perturbed and in need of some assistance.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_SEQ_00<tab>格闘士ギルドに出入りする商人ジャジャクタは、ギルドに納品する革製品の材料の採集を、冒険者に頼みたいらしい。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_SEQ_01<tab>Jajakuta has received an order from the Pugilists' Guild for several gloves and harnesses, but he lacks the materials needed to craft them. Gather the pelts he requires by heading to central Thanalan and culling snapping shrews.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_SEQ_01<tab>中央ザナラーンに生息している「スナッピング・シュルー」から、「シュルーの粗皮」を5体分、手に入れよう。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_SEQ_02<tab>You have gathered the five shrew pelts Jajakuta requested. Deliver them to him outside the Pugilists' Guild.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_SEQ_02<tab>シュルーの粗皮を集め終えた。格闘士ギルド前にいる「ジャジャクタ」に報告しよう。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_SEQ_03<tab>Having delivered the pelts, you can now sleep soundly in the knowledge that those hapless shrews will live on forever in the instruments of war their hides are destined to become.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_SEQ_03<tab>良質なシュルーの粗皮を無事、届けることができた。格闘士ギルドとも、お得意様として、これからも商売を続けていけるだろう。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_TODO_00<tab>Collect shrew pelts from snapping shrews in central Thanalan.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_TODO_00<tab>スナッピング・シュルーからシュルーの粗皮を入手

source: TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_TODO_01<tab>Report to Jajakuta outside the Pugilists' Guild.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_TODO_01<tab>格闘士ギルド前にいるジャジャクタに報告

source: TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_JAJAKUTA_000<tab>Tell me, what brings you here, friend? Hm? Looking for a bit of work, perhaps? Some small job to add a little weight to that coinpurse of yours, hm?
target:
TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_JAJAKUTA_000格闘士ギルドに立ち寄った冒険者よ。
ここで会ったのも何かの縁、頼みごとを受けてくれるか？

source: TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_JAJAKUTA_001<tab>Well, you're in luck! The pugilists have just placed an order with me for several of the leather gloves and harnesses they use for sparring.
target:
TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_JAJAKUTA_001私は格闘士ギルドに出入りしている商人なんだが、
練習に使用するグローブや胸当てなど、
格闘用革製品の大量発注を受けたのだ。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_JAJAKUTA_002<tab>But the Traders are cruel, for I find myself lacking the hides required. Would that I had the pelts of a few snapping shrews...
target:
TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_JAJAKUTA_002しかし……今、材料が在庫切れでな。
「スナッピング・シュルー」という魔物の皮は、
良質な革製品の材料になる。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_JAJAKUTA_003<tab>What say you, friend, hm? Care to help a merchant down on his luck, hm? Bring me five snapping shrew pelts and I promise to make it worth your while. You can find the creatures roaming central Thanalan.
target:
TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_JAJAKUTA_003中央ザナラーンにいるスナッピング・シュルーを倒し、
「シュルーの粗皮」をとってきてくれ。
数は5つほどあればいい。頼んだぞ。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_JAJAKUTA_013<tab>Back already, are you? Come, let us see what you've brought.
target:
TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_JAJAKUTA_013おっ、帰ってきたか。
どうだ、成果はあったか？

source: TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_JAJAKUTA_010<tab>Exceptional! These are fine shrew pelts indeed! Well done, my friend.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_JAJAKUTA_010<tab>おお、こいつは良質な「シュルーの粗皮」だ！

source: TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_JAJAKUTA_011<tab>The Pugilists' Guild is among my largest clients. I fear what would have come to pass had this order been delayed any longer.
target:
TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_JAJAKUTA_011格闘士ギルドは大口の取引先だからな。
納品が遅れて仕事に穴でも開いたら、大損失だ。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_JAJAKUTA_012<tab>Take this, hm? You've more than earned it.
target:
TEXT_SUBWIL015_00163_JAJAKUTA_012助かったよ、こいつはほんの礼だ。
とっておいてくれ。
